title: Ask.Video Reason 4 Tutorials
description: Making music should be as easy as powering up a computer, loading up a powerful piece of music software, and getting down to business. And it is. Reason version 4 is a virtual studio rack with all the tools and instruments you will need to turn your ideas into music. It&#039;s more than just a set of excellent synths and effects. It&#039;s a complete music studio system. Join Audio Expert and Producer, Kenneth Braithwaite, as he walks you through this powerful application. To get started, click on one of the movie links.
